<div class="static-hero"><h1>Privacy Policy</h1><p>Last updated: April 20, 2026</p></div>
<div class="static-content">
  <p>FatSwitchDiet.com ("we", "us") is committed to protecting your privacy. This policy explains how we collect and use your information.</p>
  <h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>
  <ul><li><strong>Usage Data:</strong> Pages visited, browser type, device info, IP address via analytics.</li><li><strong>Contact Data:</strong> Name and email if you contact us.</li><li><strong>Cookies:</strong> For analytics and advertising (see Section 4).</li></ul>
  <h2>2. Google AdSense</h2>
  <p>We use Google AdSense to display ads. Google uses cookies to serve personalised ads based on your browsing history. You can opt out at <a href="https://www.google.com/settings/ads" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Google Ads Settings</a>.</p>
  <h2>3. Google Analytics</h2>
  <p>We use Google Analytics to analyse site usage. You can opt out via the <a href="https://tools.google.com/dlpage/gaoptout" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Google Analytics opt-out add-on</a>.</p>
  <h2>4. Cookies</h2>
  <p>We use necessary, analytics, and advertising cookies. You can control cookies in your browser settings.</p>
  <h2>5. Your Rights</h2>
  <p>You may request access, correction, or deletion of your data. Contact us at privacy@fatswitchdiet.com.</p>
  <h2>6. Contact</h2>
  <p><a href="/contact">Contact Page</a> · privacy@fatswitchdiet.com</p>
</div>
